^ These should all be located in a main config file ^

Users
uuid|login|pwhash|email
VARCHAR(uuid):128   - this'll be a sha1 hash of the login (refer to examples)
VARCHAR(login):25  - this is just the login name
VARCHAR(pwhash):255 - a hash of password using their uuid as seed
VARCHAR(email):89  - their email

Bios
uuid|image|bio


